    { title: "Techs sell, but it stays in their heads", description: "Add-ons and recommendations happen verbally — no estimate, no follow-up, no upsell pipeline." },
    { title: "Reviews don't show up", description: "Happy customers don't think to leave a review unless asked at the right moment. Local search rankings stall." },
    { title: "Recurring service / maintenance plans go cold", description: "PM agreements sit in a binder, nobody schedules them, and the recurring revenue you sold quietly churns." },
    { title: "You can't see truck profitability", description: "Hours, parts and revenue per tech, per truck, per type of call live in scattered spreadsheets. Coaching is gut feel." },
  ]}
