  ]}
  faqs={[
    { question: "Do you replace ServiceTitan or Housecall Pro?", answer: "Usually no — we wrap them. We integrate via API to fix the spots where FSM platforms don't quite fit your business: call-handling flow, reviews, PM scheduling, custom dashboards. For smaller shops we sometimes build a custom FSM from scratch." },
    { question: "Can it handle after-hours and overflow calls?", answer: "Yes. We integrate with answering services or build a custom AI-assisted overflow flow that captures the booking, gathers the right info and pushes it to dispatch ready for morning." },
    { question: "Will dispatchers actually use it?", answer: "We design the dispatch board around how your dispatchers actually think — by drive time, tech skill, parts availability — not a generic Kanban. We onboard dispatchers personally during pilot." },
    { question: "Does it sync to QuickBooks?", answer: "Yes. Invoices, payments, deposits and parts cost sync to QuickBooks Online or Desktop. Bookkeepers keep their flow." },
